[SOFTER] Nobody issued a memo about it.

171
00:13:07,095 --> 00:13:12,974
Nobody held a meeting. The closet simply
worked better, and the people who used it

172
00:13:12,974 --> 00:13:17,836
noticed in the way you notice that a
