174
00:13:21,538 --> 00:13:26,400
Sandra, the receptionist on the ground
floor, began leaving a cup of coffee on

175
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:31,515
Owen's cart every morning. She placed it
in the same spot — the flat space between

176
00:13:31,515 --> 00:13:36,441
