179
00:13:46,481 --> 00:13:51,091
black, always in the same ceramic mug
with a faded university crest on the

180
00:13:51,091 --> 00:13:56,079
side, and Owen always drank it slowly —
the way a man drinks when he has learned

181
00:13:56,079 --> 00:14:01,131
that even small things deserve attention
