185
00:14:13,703 --> 00:14:19,859
right away. But by the third week, there
was a current of quiet recognition moving

186
00:14:19,859 --> 00:14:25,712
through the building — the kind that
builds not from any single impressive act

187
00:14:25,712 --> 00:14:31,488
but from the accumulated evidence of
someone who does his work well and never

188
00:14:31,488 --> 00:14:36,809
once asks you to notice. A logistics
analyst on the sixth floor started

189
00:14:36,809 --> 00:14:42,358
